## Lab Grown 1 Carat Pear Shaped Diamond Ring

Lab grown 1ct pear shaped diamond rings at Blue Nile use IGI, GIA, or GCAL certified lab pear diamonds that are physically and chemically identical to natural pear diamonds. The lab stones at 1ct reach D-VVS1 grade for $1,006 and D-IF for $1,548 — grades that cost $6,230 and $7,578 in natural GIA equivalents. The complete lab grown 1ct pear ring, stone plus setting, is achievable under $2,000 with a 14K solitaire.

